title: DON'T WASTE YOUR TIME
itunes:title: DON'T WASTE YOUR TIME
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
START TODAY NOT TOMORROW! Are you ready for your life to begin? Now is your time! Listen to this every morning and your life will begin to change. One of the Best Motivational Speeches Ever featuring Pastor and Motivational Speaker Brian M. Bullock (https://bit.ly/BrianBullockMotiversity). Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), and Succession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube).
